{"word":"περικαλυπτέα","slug":"περικαλυπτέα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>περικαλυπτέα</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:verbal Adjective'>verb. <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a></a> of <a href='S:περικαλύπτω'><el>περικαλύπτω</el></a>\n<p/><i>one must muffle</i> or <i>wrap oneself up</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <el>περικᾰλύπτω</el>\n"}]}